Maintainer: Henrique Sposito <henrique.sposito@graduateinstitute.ch>
Description: A set of tools for wrangling and annotating
    different types of political texts within R.
    The package also introduces Urgency Analysis,
    a new method for the analysis of urgency in political texts.
